column1: # Sampling station data to accompany: Carbon isotopic fractionation in organic matter production consistent with benthic community composition across a coral reef flat
# Contact the corresponding author David A. Koweek with any questions (dkoweek@carnegiescience.edu)
# Line = Front (F); Middle (M); or Back (B) line
# Line_Position = Position of each sample on each line referenced from the center of each line (meters; negative values are south of the midpoint)
# d13C_DIC = Stable isotopic composition of DIC (relative to VPDB standard)
